@startuml
title D2: View Patient's Historic Medical Record

actor "Doctor" as Doctor
participant "Frontend (UI)\n(MedicalHistory.tsx)" as UI
participant "MedicalReportController\n(app/routers/reports.py)" as API
participant "CRUD Layer\n(crud.py)" as CRUD
database "PostgreSQL\nDatabase" as DB

Doctor -> UI: Click on specific Patient
activate UI

UI -> API: GET /medical_reports/
activate API

API -> CRUD: get_patient_medical_history(patient_id)
activate CRUD

CRUD -> DB: SELECT * FROM medical_reports\nWHERE patient_id = {id}
activate DB

DB --> CRUD: Return list of reports\n(Notes, Diagnosis, Rx)
deactivate DB

CRUD --> API: Return List[MedicalReport]
deactivate CRUD

API --> UI: Return JSON data
deactivate API

UI -> UI: Format history data
UI --> Doctor: Display Medical History View
deactivate UI

@enduml